## Design Considerations

### Design System Compliance
- **Colors:** Use semantic tokens (bg-surface-*, text-text-*, border-border-*)
- **Components:** Bento cards for form cards, gradient buttons
- **Field styling:** Consistent with existing inputs (Notes editor, Task editor)
- **Typography:** Inter font stack, standard sizes
- **Spacing:** 4px base unit (gap-2, gap-4, p-4, etc.)
- **Dark Mode:** All components dark-mode compatible

### Field Type Priorities
**Phase 1 (MVP):**
- Text, Number, Date, Select, Checkbox, TextArea

**Phase 2 (Future):**
- Time, MultiSelect, Radio, Rating, Scale

### Performance
- **Bundle Size Impact:** ~50-60KB for all form components
- **Lazy Loading:** All form pages lazy-loaded
- **Optimization:** FormRenderer memoized, field components pure

### Accessibility
- **Keyboard Nav:** Tab through fields, Enter to submit
- **Screen Reader:** All fields have proper labels, ARIA roles
- **Focus Management:** Clear focus states, focus trap in modals
- **Validation:** Error messages announced to screen readers

