## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| Form builder UX too complex | Medium | Medium | Start simple (list-based, not visual canvas) |
| Field types incomplete | Low | Low | Start with core 6 types, add more later |
| Bundle size increase | Medium | Low | Lazy-load all pages, code-split field components |
| CSV export fails on edge cases | Low | Medium | Test with all field types, handle nulls |
| Performance with large forms | Low | Low | Memoize components, virtualize if >50 fields |

